1
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:11,950
♪Obsessions penned
into an everlasting love♪

2
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Affections gently linger
around fingertips♪

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:23,140
♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:28,520
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

5
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:30,900
♪May transient frost♪

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,690
♪Persist through obstacles for love♪

7
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:40,330
♪I wait for you to look back
in this rocky life♪

8
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,550
♪I can stay for the promise♪

9
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:46,180
♪Despite seasons recur♪

10
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,760
♪The love deep within
will transcend time♪

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:57,500
[Secrets of the Shadow Sect]

12
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:00,820
[Episode 1]

13
00:01:06,050 --> 00:01:09,470
[Xuantian House]

14
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:39,940
Young Master.

15
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:41,740
Are you satisfied

16
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,620
with the Pipa dance I just learned?

17
00:01:49,020 --> 00:01:49,900
Yes.

18
00:01:50,540 --> 00:01:51,620
Very much so.

19
00:01:53,140 --> 00:01:54,540
You may leave.

20
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:13,620
Yingshi.

21
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:15,300
Must you really push me to death?

22
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:17,220
What do you mean?

23
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,140
Only five candidates

24
00:02:19,140 --> 00:02:19,980
can graduate from the Shadow Sect.

25
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,300
Between you and me,

26
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:24,580
one must die.

27
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:26,260
In tonight's life-and-death trial,

28
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,180
why did you

29
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:28,500
come after me

30
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:29,780
out of thirteen people?

31
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:40,060
Needless to say,

32
00:02:41,260 --> 00:02:42,780
you don't deserve to live.

33
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:57,780
Well.

34
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:00,580
Who could be so heartless

35
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,860
to send you to kill me?

36
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:05,340
I will be upset

37
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:07,020
if your hand is stained with blood.

38
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:11,740
What a delicate face you have.

39
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:14,140
However,

40
00:03:14,140 --> 00:03:15,380
it has ruined my day.

41
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:16,620
Why don't you

42
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,220
smile at me?

43
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:19,900
I can let you go

44
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:21,020
if your smile is sweet.

45
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:21,940
How does that sound?

46
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:24,900
Young Master.

47
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:40,020
I shouldn't have been so careless

48
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,260
and let a trouble like you

49
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,740
survive these years.

50
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:46,660
I survived

51
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:48,300
because I earned it.

52
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,740
Wake her up

53
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:08,380
and interrogate her strictly.

54
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:14,340
I, Yingshi,

55
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:16,020
offer greetings, Sir.

56
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,620
Whoever joins the Shadow Sect

57
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:19,900
has to endure desperate, deadly training

58
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:21,340
for ten years.

59
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,540
You outperformed others

60
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:24,700
in the life-and-death trial.

61
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:26,860
Now you have graduated,

62
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:28,820
have you decided

63
00:04:29,940 --> 00:04:31,700
whom to pledge your loyalty to?

64
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:43,000
[Lingtian Palace]

65
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:44,780
Bring the folded fan

66
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:45,500
for us to see.

67
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:46,500
Young Master gave me this.

68
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:47,420
Don't dirty it.

69
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:48,700
The silk gown is gorgeous.

70
00:04:48,700 --> 00:04:49,300
I will bring it here.

71
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,100
Stay here.

72
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:50,900
Wait for me.

73
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:00,620
Such a heavenly tune.

74
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:02,540
Watch where you are going.

75
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,300
Who is he?

76
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,460
A new shadow guard?

77
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,740
He's quite good-looking.

78
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:07,740
I wonder

79
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:09,140
if Young Master would take him.

80
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:12,020
[Xuantian House]

81
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:31,980
Young Master.

82
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,260
What's wrong?

83
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:34,900
Is the room

84
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:35,940
dirty?

85
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:37,020
No.

86
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,940
Something dirty stains on me yesterday.

87
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:41,740
It doesn't feel clean enough.

88
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:43,820
What's the matter?

89
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:46,260
It's time new shadow guards graduate

90
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:47,220
and seek for masters.

91
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:48,260
The Shadow Sect

92
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:49,460
has sent a shadow guard over again
this year.

93
00:05:49,860 --> 00:05:51,260
He is waiting outside.

94
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:51,940
I don't want any.

95
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:53,140
As usual,

96
00:05:53,380 --> 00:05:54,140
send him back.

97
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:56,220
I told him.

98
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:57,060
But he refuses to leave

99
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,340
and insists on seeing you.

100
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:02,020
Very well.

101
00:06:02,580 --> 00:06:03,860
Let him wait, then.

102
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:05,940
Yes.

103
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,620
He hasn't left yet.

104
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:39,620
He has been standing here
for almost a day.

105
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:43,620
Hurry and bring dinner into the room.

106
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:44,820
Yes.

107
00:06:51,660 --> 00:06:53,460
The former lady of the sect leader

108
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:55,340
is the only disciple of

109
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:57,060
the Feiyun Sect's chief.

110
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:58,860
After she passed away,

111
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:01,100
the exclusive technique of Feiyun Sect,

112
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,420
the Wanxin Manual, was lost.

113
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:03,860
The only manuscript

114
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:07,740
should be hidden by Young Master.

115
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:10,260
Her abode

116
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,340
may seem loosely guarded,
but it's airtight internally.

117
00:07:12,340 --> 00:07:13,660
Over the years,

118
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:15,740
no one has ever gotten in.

119
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:18,660
I want you

120
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:21,420
to recognize Ling Xuan as your master

121
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,820
and find the Wanxin Manual.

122
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,700
After obtaining it...

123
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:32,220
I will do my very best.

124
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,820
It seems the fresh graduate this year

125
00:07:37,820 --> 00:07:39,460
has quite some patience.

126
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,940
Did the Shadow Sect send you over

127
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:56,100
to stand guard

128
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:57,820
like a dummy?

129
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:11,660
Forgive me, Young Master.

130
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:12,860
My name is Yingshi.

131
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,260
Please accept

132
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,180
my name token

133
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,340
and take me as your guard.

134
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:18,740
I will be loyal and devoted.

135
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:22,780
Xuantian House only keeps beauties,

136
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:24,020
not guards.

137
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:25,660
You may leave.

138
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:29,140
I'm a First Class graduate.

139
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,940
Please reconsider, Young Master.

140
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:46,460
I'm the young master of
the Lingtian Palace.

141
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:48,340
I'm safe here.

142
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:49,660
Why do I need you?

143
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,660
Why haven't you left yet?

144
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:58,860
Young Master.

145
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:01,260
Do you remember

146
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,540
the pair of siblings you saved
ten years ago?

147
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:07,140
You had someone
to cure the younger sister

148
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:09,580
and found a decent family to adopt her.

149
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:11,180
Then, you brought the older brother

150
00:09:11,180 --> 00:09:12,500
to Lingtian Palace.

151
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,100
Do you remember anything?

152
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,140
I can save her.

153
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:48,500
But you should trade it for your life.

154
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:49,580
Will you?

155
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:53,140
Yes.

156
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:54,540
If so, I must leave a mark

157
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:55,580
on you.

158
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,260
This wound still seems so scary

159
00:09:58,700 --> 00:10:00,060
after ten years.

160
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:02,420
I never thought you were still alive.

161
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:04,900
You managed to leave Shadow Sect

162
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:06,060
alive.

163
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:08,260
I swore with my blood.

164
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:10,140
I dare not to go back on my word.

165
00:10:13,220 --> 00:10:15,020
The Shadow Sect is a deadly battleground

166
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,900
where battling and killing

167
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:18,700
occur daily over ten years.

168
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:21,620
You should hate me.

169
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,780
Why did you come to offer your service?

170
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,500
If it weren't for you,

171
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,860
my sister and I would
have been dead long ago.

172
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,500
I wouldn't have lived until now.

173
00:10:34,020 --> 00:10:34,980
To think

174
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:36,740
that there are silly yet grateful people

175
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:38,860
like you.

176
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:44,860
Instead of being grateful,

177
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:46,380
I would say

178
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:48,580
that I gave you my life

179
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,500
back then.

180
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:50,580
Young Master.

181
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,300
Do you

182
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:55,020
still want me?

183
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:13,060
I do.

184
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:21,740
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

185
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:25,340
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

186
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,620
♪Goodbye♪

187
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:31,660
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

188
00:11:32,940 --> 00:11:36,270
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

189
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:39,980
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

190
00:11:40,380 --> 00:11:42,660
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

191
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:44,260
♪I only wish your eyes♪

192
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:47,340
♪As pure as snow♪
